<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1003] XPathEntityprocessor must allow slurping all text from a given xml node and its children</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1003</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;take an example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;xhtml:p&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;This text is 
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;xhtml:b&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;bold&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/xhtml:b&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; and this text is 
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;xhtml:u&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;underlined&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/xhtml:u&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;!
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/xhtml:p&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It may be useful to get all the text from all the tags in &amp;lt;xhtml: p&amp;gt; ignoring the tag names .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the configuration of the field may look like&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;field column=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;para&quot;&lt;/span&gt; xpath=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/p&quot;&lt;/span&gt; flatten=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;true&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
